## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="1d8ec-105">建立時，不會保留使用者的主體帳戶。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1d8ec-105">The user principal account is not persisted when it is created.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1d8ec-106">若要儲存帳戶，請呼叫<xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal.Save%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1d8ec-106">To save the account, call the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal.Save%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="1d8ec-107">下列程式碼範例會連線到 LDAP 網域"fabrikam.com"的使用者名稱和密碼，初始化<xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext>建構函式以 「 系統管理員 」 和 「 securelyStoredPassword。 」</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1d8ec-107">The following code example connects to the LDAP domain "fabrikam.com" with the username and password initialized in the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> constructor to "administrator" and "securelyStoredPassword."</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="1d8ec-108">在此範例中，使用者名稱和電子郵件地址，例如設定的屬性中指定的容器下建立<xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext>建構函式:"CN = Users，DC = fabrikam，DC = com。 」</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1d8ec-108">The properties set in the example, such as user name and email address, are created under the container specified in the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> constructor: "CN=Users,DC=fabrikam,DC=com."</span></span>  
  
```  
  
PrincipalContext ctx = new PrincipalContext(  
                                         ContextType.Domain,  
                                         "fabrikam.com",   
                                         "CN=Users,DC=fabrikam,DC=com",  
                                         "administrator",   
                                         "securelyStoredPassword");   
  
UserPrincipal usr = new UserPrincipal(ctx);  
  
usr.Name = "Jim Daly";  
usr.Description = "This is the user account for Jim Daly";  
usr.EmailAddress = "jimdaly@fabrikam.com";  
usr.SetPassword("securelyStoredPassword");  
usr.Save();  
  
usr.Dispose();  
ctx.Dispose();   
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="1d8ec-160">下列程式碼會連線到本機電腦存放區。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1d8ec-160">The following code connects to the local computer store.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1d8ec-161">因為在未指定認證<xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext>建構函式，會使用目前執行緒執行的使用者認證。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1d8ec-161">Since the credentials are not specified in the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> constructor, the credentials of the user running the current thread are used.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="1d8ec-162">若要尋找之使用者的 SamAccountName 「 來賓 」 執行搜尋。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1d8ec-162">A search is performed to find the user who has SamAccountName "Guest".</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="1d8ec-163">如果找到使用者，則會檢查以判斷是否已啟用這位使用者的帳戶。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1d8ec-163">If the user is found, a check is performed to determine whether this user's account is enabled.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1d8ec-164">如果帳戶未啟用，範例程式碼就會啟用它。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1d8ec-164">If the account is not enabled, the example code enables it.</span></span>  
  
```  
PrincipalContext ctx = new PrincipalContext(ContextType.Machine);  
  
UserPrincipal usr = UserPrincipal.FindByIdentity(ctx,   
                                           IdentityType.SamAccountName,   
                                           "Guest");  
  
if(usr != null)  
{  
    if (usr.Enabled == false)  
        usr.Enabled = true;  
  
    usr.Save();  
    usr.Dispose();  
}  
ctx.Dispose();   
```
